PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774627872
OL,3,CHundreds of BMA doctors' union staff
OL,4,Cwalk out on strike in pay dispute
OL,6,FStriking BMA staff will return to work
OL,7,Fat 11.59pm on March 28.
OL,9,FThe union's chief executive, Rachel
OL,10,FPodolak, said: "We remain committed to
OL,11,Fnegotiations with the GMB to work
OL,12,Ftowards a resolution and want to
OL,13,Fcontinue open and meaningful dialogue
OL,14,Fin the hope of reaching a settlement
OL,15,Fthat is acceptable to staff and
OL,16,Fsustainable for the organisation."
OL,26,@rD@POUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
