PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774627872
OL,3,CHundreds of BMA doctors' union staff
OL,4,Cwalk out on strike in pay dispute
OL,6,FShe said the BMA has increased its
OL,7,Foriginal offer of a 2% pay rise to
OL,8,F2.75%, plus #1,000 for workers on
OL,9,Flower pay, enhanced paid paternity
OL,10,Fleave and three days more annual leave.
OL,12,F"We are confident that the overall
OL,13,Fpackage of pay and benefits for staff
OL,14,Fat the BMA is highly competitive with
OL,15,Four comparator organisations," she
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
