PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774627872
OL,3,CHundreds of BMA doctors' union staff
OL,4,Cwalk out on strike in pay dispute
OL,6,FBMA staff will also strike on April 6
OL,7,Fand 7, which is during the resident
OL,8,Fdoctor walkouts.
OL,10,FThe latest round of industrial action
OL,11,Fby medics represents the 15th strike
OL,12,Fby resident doctors since 2023.
OL,14,FIt has been estimated that it could
OL,15,Fcost the health service up to #300
OL,16,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
