PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774627872
OL,3,CHundreds of BMA doctors' union staff
OL,4,Cwalk out on strike in pay dispute
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, BMA resident doctors
OL,7,Fcommittee chairman Dr Jack Fletcher
OL,8,Fsaid the union had been "negotiating
OL,9,Fin good faith for weeks" and had been
OL,10,F"making good progress", but accused
OL,11,Fthe government of beginning to "shift
OL,12,Fthe goalposts".
OL,14,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,15,Fsaid resident doctors have until
OL,16,FThursday to reconsider strike action
OL,17,For the government will "consume the
OL,18,Fmoney set aside for this deal" to
OL,19,Fminimise disruption.
